=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-md\" href=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/contact-us\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Get Started<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8860b43\" data-id=\"8860b43\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee6db11 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ee6db11\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"679\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Role-of-Patent-Illustration-An-art-of-Patent-Draftsman-in-Patents.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2250\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Role-of-Patent-Illustration-An-art-of-Patent-Draftsman-in-Patents.png 679w, https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Role-of-Patent-Illustration-An-art-of-Patent-Draftsman-in-Patents-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83afdb5 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"83afdb5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bdbba92 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bdbba92\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What is Patent Filing?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0e094c3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0e094c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a process whereby an individual applies to a patent office to seek legal protection for his or her invention. This step is important to enable the inventor or the applicant to have exclusive control of the invention where no other person is allowed to make, use, or sell it without the consent of the inventor or applicant. In the case of the business entities and the inventors, an application for seeking a patent is an important tool in their armoury to safeguard the property of the innovations created by them and in addition to that sustain a competitive advantage in the market.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3977565 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3977565\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-wider\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-df9268d\" data-id=\"df9268d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-c101fc2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c101fc2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-wider\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-f32e4d7\" data-id=\"f32e4d7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3cd62a9 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3cd62a9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Patent Filing Process<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18bbe8c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"18bbe8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Filing a patent is essential for several reasons:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-6e9db91 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"6e9db91\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-custom\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-25 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-363875f\" data-id=\"363875f\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-633958b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"633958b\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-306a033 tr\" data-id=\"306a033\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71e8155 elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon\" data-id=\"71e8155\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon\">\n\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon-down-arrow\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24f013a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"24f013a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Legal Protection<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-176eef4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"176eef4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After the filing of the patent and after it has been granted, the inventor is given legal backing. It implies that the patent owner can sue anybody who uses the patented invention.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-25 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-6e7c894\" data-id=\"6e7c894\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-f33e779 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f33e779\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-1a50458\" data-id=\"1a50458\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d9f5bf elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon\" data-id=\"6d9f5bf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon\">\n\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon-down-arrow\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb29c4b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"eb29c4b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Market Exclusivity<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c064fc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0c064fc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Patents provide the inventor with a legal monopoly to exploit the invention commercially in the marketplace.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-25 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-c02769b\" data-id=\"c02769b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-cf86225 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"cf86225\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-f0dee33\" data-id=\"f0dee33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c187719 elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon\" data-id=\"c187719\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon\">\n\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon-down-arrow\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f57f8c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7f57f8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Monetisation Opportunities<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db31ff6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"db31ff6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A patent gives a lot of opportunity to the inventor as the inventor can license out the technology to others or sell outright the patent.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-25 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-bd66301\" data-id=\"bd66301\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-aef2114 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"aef2114\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-05d8210\" data-id=\"05d8210\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d713a3 elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon\" data-id=\"5d713a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon\">\n\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon-down-arrow\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3709eb7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3709eb7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Increased Valuation<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f6116da elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f6116da\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To the business entity, the acquisition and development of a strong patent undertaking can act as a booster in the enhancement of the worth of the company to its investors and partners.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-443129e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"443129e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc8e946 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bc8e946\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-833ef87 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"833ef87\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98ba8ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"98ba8ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Activities that go into filing a patent<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-47284fb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"47284fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Some of the activities that go into filing a patent include fundamentals of patenting procedures and patent prosecution costs. <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Filing a patent involves several key steps, each of which must be carefully followed to ensure the application is successful:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bbf8b9e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bbf8b9e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Conduct a Patent Search:<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When seeking to get a patent for an invention it is good practice to carry out a patent search to ensure that the invention doesn\u2019t have a previous patent. This step assists in preventing possible legal disputes and also makes the invention so developed to qualify for a patent.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Prepare the Patent Application:<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The next process is to prepare the patent prosecution document also known as the patent application. This document is an extended description of the invention with drawings if needed and the claims that will describe the protection that is being sought. The application could be a provisional application in which an early filing date is obtained or a non-provisional application containing full description of the invention.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Submit the Patent Application:<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, this must be done after the application has first been prepared to be submitted to the relevant patent office. This in the case of India would be the Indian Patent Office. Application can be made online or on paper and the date of application is very important as it determines the application\u2019s standing in terms of priority of invention.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Examination Process:<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They go through an examination stage where a patent examiner conducts a search in order to ascertain that the application meets all legal provisions. This involves having a verification of the invention for novelty in addition to the invention\u2019s non-obviousness or inventive step as well as industrial applicability.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Addressing Objections:<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The applicant is allowed to respond to any issues that the examiner may have with the application by making some explanations or changes. Thus, one could conclude that the main reason for successfully coming through the mentioned stages is the ability to meet the objections that follow.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Patent Grant:<\/b><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thus after all the objections have been addressed the invention is deemed to have complied with all the requirements and thus a patent is given. This provides the patent holder monopoly over the invention for a particular time \u2013 usually, 20 years from the date the application for the patent was filed.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-138c8be e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"138c8be\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-691be07 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"691be07\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"448\" height=\"336\" src=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/asset-v1_EBC-Learningregistration-of-patents2023type@assetblock@registration-of-patents-tile.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2456\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/asset-v1_EBC-Learningregistration-of-patents2023type@assetblock@registration-of-patents-tile.webp 448w, https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/asset-v1_EBC-Learningregistration-of-patents2023type@assetblock@registration-of-patents-tile-300x225.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9d1fab6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9d1fab6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f54c41d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f54c41d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-724b94b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"724b94b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8bb4ed3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8bb4ed3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"628\" src=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/patents-as-collateral.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2457\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/patents-as-collateral.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/patents-as-collateral-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/patents-as-collateral-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.trademarkindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/patents-as-collateral-768x402.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b16ef27 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b16ef27\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5815bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d5815bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tips for Successful Patent Filing<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-54f920f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"54f920f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><b>Be Thorough:<\/b><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition, there are certain recommendations required to be followed while filing the patent application, that an applicant should be very professional and specific. Legal descriptions are specific and thus minimise the possibility of objections and move the approval faster.<\/span><\/p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><b>Consult an Expert:<\/b><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Patent law is tricky. A patent attorney is also beneficial in this process to lead the way and avoid common pitfalls that will lead to the rejection of the application.<\/span><\/p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><b>File Early:<\/b><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indeed, timing is everything in the world of patents. Filing early means your invention will be protected by a priority date and it gives you a head start against your competitors.<\/span><\/p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><b>Maintain Your Patent:<\/b><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Patents need regular upkeep. This is crucial to remember, as it is easy to have your rights taken away if you do not pay for maintenance on time \u2013 but do not worry, it\u2019s not all for nought if you have been putting in the effort:<\/span><\/p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><b>Use Online Registration:<\/b><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The procedures for the registration of patents in the online platform are however speedy and efficient. It can assist you to apply faster, keep the application organised, and monitor all processes without any difficulties.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Patent Filing \u2013 TrademarkIndia Get Started What is Patent Filing? It is a process whereby an individual applies to a patent office to seek legal protection for his or her invention. This step is important to enable the inventor or the applicant to have exclusive control of the invention where no other person is allowed [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":891,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1880","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Patent Filing - Experts in Patent filing IPR Law firm Ahmedabad | Trademark India<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Trademark India, an IPR law firm in Ahmedabad, Surat, Jaipur, Indore, offers expert p